================
About the script
================

This script used for remove host from nagios configuration.

------
How to
------

You have two ways to use this script.

-p specify the path of faurecia-nagios-configuration if you have more than one repo on your computer.Or you can ignore it, the script can find it automatic.
-n specify the hostname.
-f specify the filename.

eg:
./remove.py -n host1 -n host2 -p /home/chengca/faurecia-nagios-configuration

./remove.py -f host.txt -p /home/chengca/faurecia-nagios-configurationu
